Beverly Bayne https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beverly_Bayne 0 Beverly Bayne (born Pearl Beverly Bain) (November 11, 1894 – August 18, 1982) was an American actress who appeared in silent films beginning in 1910 in Chicago, Illinois, where she worked for Essanay Studios.
